#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/geminids.tsx:119
msgid "Whether your night air is warm or cool, a comfortable place to sit or lie back makes the experience far more enjoyable."
msgstr "Che l’aria notturna sia calda o fresca, un posto comodo dove sedersi o distendersi rende l’esperienza molto più piacevole."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/total-lunar-eclipse.tsx:64
msgid "While eclipses were once viewed as omens, today they are widely appreciated as shared moments of skywatching and wonder."
msgstr "Se un tempo le eclissi erano viste come presagi, oggi sono ampiamente apprezzate come momenti condivisi di osservazione del cielo e meraviglia."

